// Package sqlc holds the sqlc-generated CRUD bindings for the OCS
// Testbench data model.
//
// The contents are produced by `sqlc generate` from the SQL files
// under internal/store/queries (and the schema under db/migrations).
// At Task 1 of the data-model Feature only the package shell exists;
// the generated bindings are produced in Task 2.
//
// Do not edit generated files by hand — re-run `sqlc generate`.
package sqlc
